OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly dry and fine, with
OL,6,Fvariable amounts of cloud and some
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Easterly winds will
OL,8,Fgradually strengthen through the day,
OL,9,Fleading to a cooler feel, especially
OL,10,Falong eastern coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly cloudy with some
OL,13,Fpatchy rain in the north. The
OL,14,Fnortheasterly wind will increase,
OL,15,Fbecoming breezy especially along the
OL,16,Fcoast. Feeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
